    Add script to generate html version of README.md

    This makes GitHub Pages hosted docs root look like README.md on GitHub

    Add copy of github-markdown-css and its MIT license file

    Python script uses GitHub's markdown API to convert the markdown content to
    html, and then wraps the generated html content with appropriate stuff to use
    the github-markdown-css style.  Works in light and dark themes.
